{
  "stem": "5639.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I don't know where from, I swear to you, I never heard the word before, [SPEAKING GERMAN] It's the process of dehumanization.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's what I said to him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[SPEAKING GERMAN] That was the last I saw of him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there were people I met.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One girl from my town, and the first message that I got was never to have anything to do with him.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Apparently he was a- a kapo, and he was dealing with diamonds, whatever it was.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now Auschwitz, the peak of inhumanity was also a source of the greatest and deepest humanity.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "If there was a humanity there was in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The fact that somebody addressed you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We came to a barrack.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was given a bowl, an enamel, chipped, red bowl that had a hole.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my first instinct was to tip the bowl towards me so the liquid won't run out through the hole.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Later on I found out what the hole was for.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I looked around and I said, anybody has got a spoon?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there was a woman standing, to me she was old, but by that time I didn't know how I look anymore.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she said to me in Yiddish, eat my child, eat, that's all what you'll ever get.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I put my lips to that bowl, at first my stomach rumbled.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I looked around, and everybody was lapping up like dogs, like animals.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so did I.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I mean that was an act of humanity-- a stranger.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "A stranger that helped you to stand up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "A stranger that moved close to you to give you a bit of warmth.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "A stranger that you never remembered his face.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "A person that you saw today and she disappeared.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
